### BOARDS ROUTES

### GET ALL BOARDS
GET http://localhost:4000/boards HTTP/1.1

### GET SINGLE BOARD
GET http://localhost:4000/boards/1 HTTP/1.1

### ADD NEW BOARD
POST http://localhost:4000/boards HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "NEW BOARD",
  "columns": [
    {
      "title": "column one",
      "order": 0
    }
  ]
}

### DELETE SINGLE BOARD
DELETE http://localhost:4000/boards/2 HTTP/1.1

### UPDATE SINGLE BOARD
PUT http://localhost:4000/boards/1  HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "UPDATED BOARD",
  "columns": [
    {
      "title": "column one",
      "order": 0
    },
    {
      "title": "column TWO",
      "order": 1
    }
  ]
}


